title: 700. 32 Super Sophomores to Watch
itunes:title: 700. 32 Super Sophomores to Watch
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. On this special show, the guys give their takeaways from Green Bay Packers quarterback Aaron Rodgers' recent press conference. Next, the duo give a list of 32 super sophomores to watch out for, as they discuss one per team.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
